---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Zones d'intervention" 
  description="Vartista intervient dans toutes les communes de Bruxelles pour vos urgences plomberie et débouchage."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1>Zones d'intervention</h1>
      <p>Nos plombiers couvrent l'ensemble de la région de Bruxelles-Capitale</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="locations-wrapper">
        <div class="locations-content">
          <h2>Intervention Rapide à Bruxelles</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Pour toute urgence plomberie ou débouchage, la réactivité est primordiale. C'est pourquoi nous avons organisé nos équipes pour pouvoir intervenir en 30 minutes dans toutes les communes de la région de Bruxelles.
          </p>
          
          <div class="communes-grid">
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Bruxelles (1000)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Schaerbeek (1030)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Etterbeek (1040)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Ixelles (1050)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Saint-Gilles (1060)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Anderlecht (1070)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Molenbeek (1080)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Uccle (1180)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Forest (1190)
            </div>
            <div class="commune-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              Woluwe (1200)
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-box glass-card mt-5">
            <h3>Vous êtes dans les environs ?</h3>
            <p>Nous intervenons également dans la périphérie bruxelloise. Contactez-nous pour vérifier notre disponibilité.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">Vérifier la disponibilité</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="map-container glass-card">
          <!-- Placeholder pour une carte interactive ou image de Bruxelles -->
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559524021-0268578b9f1a?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Carte de Bruxelles" class="map-img" />
          <div class="map-overlay">
            <div class="pulse-marker"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .locations-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .locations-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .mb-4 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mt-4 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mt-5 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .communes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .commune-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .commune-item:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .cta-box {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
  }

  .map-container {
    position: relative;
    padding: 1rem;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .map-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .map-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .pulse-marker {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pulse-marker::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: -10px;
    right: -10px;
    bottom: -10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--primary);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% {
      transform: scale(0.5);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(3);
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
